@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="card shadow-sm">
    <div class="card-header bg-white">
        <h2 class="text-secondary">@ViewData["Title"]</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <p class="lead">
            This page outlines the policy regarding the collection, use, and protection of your personal information within the Disaster Alleviation Foundation web application, aligning with global and local data protection standards.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-4" />

        <h4 class="text-primary">1. Information We Collect</h4>
        <p>
            We collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us when you register on the site, report a disaster, or make a donation. This includes:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>**Registration Data:** Full Name, Email Address, Password.</li>
            <li>**Disaster Reporting Data:** Location, Dates, Description of the incident.</li>
            <li>**Donation Data:** Donor name, Contact information, and the nature of the donation (e.g., amount of money or type of goods).</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="text-primary mt-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
        <p>
            Your information is essential for operating the foundation:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>To **Process Donations** and issue acknowledgements.</li>
            <li>To **Verify and Act** upon disaster incident reports for effective relief planning.</li>
            <li>To **Communicate** with volunteers regarding assigned tasks and schedules.</li>
            <li>To **Secure** your account and prevent fraudulent activity.</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="text-primary mt-4">3. Data Security and Protection</h4>
        <p>
            We implement robust security measures, including encryption and secure authentication, to protect your data against unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. We are committed to maintaining the confidentiality and integrity of all user information.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-5 text-muted">
            *This policy is subject to updates. Please check this page periodically for changes.*
        </p>
    </div>
</div>